        public static boolean driveStraight​(double distance,
                                    double power)
        drives the robot straight either forward or backwards
        Parameters:
        distance - : the distance in encoder ticks to travel
        power - : the power at which to drive where -1.0 is full speed backwards and 1.0 is full speed forwards
        Returns:
        returns true if the robot has driven the distance in ticks, false otherwise
